ist2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-93_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-94_">Recognise signs of radicalisation</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-96_">Take appropriate action when concerns arise
